          <title>WNBA champion invests in Bay Area sports franchise</title>
          <description><![CDATA[(KRON) – WNBA champion and Bay Area native Sabrina Ionescu was announced as an investor and commercial advisor for the Bay Football Club.  Ionescu, who is also a three-time All-Star and Olympic gold medalist, announced her involvement with Bay FC on Instagram.]]></description>
